import networkx as nx

id_type, type = int(r.id_type)-1, r.type
n = int(r.n)
k = int(r.k)
ord = int(r.ord)
dim = int(r.dim)

name = ''.join([str(n), "_graph_snn", "_k", str(k), "_dim", str(dim), type[id_type], str(ord)])
path = "../../graphs/kidney/"
gexf_graph_name = ''.join([path, name, ".gexf"])


png_graph_name = ''.join([path, name, ".png"])
png_graph_name2 = ''.join([path, name, "_2.png"])

graph = nx.read_gexf(gexf_graph_name)
